The paper deals with the problem of large scale multi agent reinforcement learning, which is a topic that falls under the categories of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), multi-agent systems (cs.MA), distributed computing (cs.DC), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper proposes a new approach to address the representation problem of the pairwise value function, which is a common issue in multi-agent reinforcement learning. Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.AI and cs.LG, followed by cs.MA, cs.DC, and cs.SY.
